      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>CAPACITY 20; USAGE 1/MINUTE</strong></p>\n<p>Immobilizers were tools sivvs used to restrain enslaved populations. They can be attached to a creature using a standard action, but the target must be helpless, unconscious, or willing. An immobilizer fills the target creature with waves of intense pain but inflicts no permanent physical harm. A creature with an immobilizer attached must attempt a DC 16 Fortitude saving throw each round at the start of their turn. On a failure, the creature is @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.2XWEujYSyryB4oHm]{Dazed}; on a success, they are @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.aAQ6SW6iK0EVq8Ce]{Staggered}. An immobilizer can be removed with a move action.</p>"
